{"tid":1219558,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講下中共侵犯香港的嚴重性","createTime":"2019-06-13T23:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T23:04:51.000Z","uid":37537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d652d9f0e4c2b9d4b2ff2674b5b52b2b62bc9c43","tid":1219558,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T23:04:51.000Z","msg":"最近(近十年),oxford一個哲學教授研究緊人類生死存亡的課題,提出global catastrophic risk model<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/X-risk-chart-en-01a.svg/500px-X-risk-chart-en-01a.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F6%2F64%2FX-risk-chart-en-01a.svg%2F500px-X-risk-chart-en-01a.svg.png&h=8e97b163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用以闡明不同事件對放人類生死存亡的嚴重程度<br />\n呢個表除左可以用於純功利主義/人類物種物理上存亡的層面之外,該教授亦將呢個model套用於倫理道德/文化傳承層面<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.existential-risk.org/concept.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.existential-risk.org%2Fconcept.html&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=b9a8aea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.existential-risk.org/concept.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以自己思考下而家呢個時勢去到一個點樣的嚴重程度<br />\n究竟係&quot;個人/地區/全球/跨世代/泛世代/全宇宙&quot;<br />\n究竟係&quot;微不足道/仍可忍受/滅絕性/地獄級&quot;"}]}